Preconditions:
- The input array `nums` must not be null.
- The input array `queries` must not be null.
- The length of the input array `nums` must be greater than or equal to the maximum value of the first element in each query in the input array `queries`.

Postconditions:
- The returned array `ans` must not be null.
- The length of the returned array `ans` must be equal to the length of the input array `queries`.
- Each element in the returned array `ans` must be an integer.